# MSC Label Maker — Environment Variables
#
# For LOCAL DEVELOPMENT:
#   Copy this file to '.env' and fill in values, then run: docker compose up --build
#
# For PORTAINER DEPLOYMENT:
#   Set these in Portainer Stack > Environment variables
